name: SOUL IN CITY
description:
Hello meatballs.

A week ago, I decided to visit all the major cities 
to select a worthy candidate 
for the position of financier in Hell.

So, Hell is here. 
Your Earth is Hell. 
Why did it never occur to you? 
Here people kill each other, betray their neighbors, 
lie, twist, show miracles of cruelty and meanness, 
die of hunger, drag out a miserable existence, 
give their daughters to prostitutes, and all world governments 
and riches are run by demons - terrible, vile and disgusting. 

No one has any salvation - even billionaires get cancer, 
and princesses are crashed in cars. 

Excuse me, but what is this if not Hell?



Soon I will come to your city, wait.
